  <description>Proximal leaves with mostly 3(–7)-rayed trichomes adaxially. Flowers: petals usually orange, sometimes orange-yellow or yellow. Fruits usually latiseptate, rarely 4-angled. Seeds 2–4 × (0.8–)1–2 mm; winged at least distally or, rarely, wing rudimentary. 2n = 36.</description>
